<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Decision Matrix Home Page</title>
	<style>
		body {
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	background-color: #f4f4f4;
	color: #333;
}

header {
	background-color: #3399ff;
	color: #fff;
	padding: 1em;
	text-align: center;
}

.hero {
	background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/977603/pexels-photo-977603.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1');
	background-size: cover;
	background-position: center center;
	height: 400px;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	align-items: center;
	justify-content: center;
	text-align: center;
	color: #fff;
}

.cta {
	display: inline-block;
	background-color: #f4511e;
	color: #fff;
	padding: 1em 2em;
	margin-top: 1em;
	text-decoration: none;
	border-radius: 5px;
	transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.cta:hover {
	background-color: #333;
}

.section {
	padding: 2em;
	display: flex;
	flex-wrap: wrap;
	justify-content: center;
	align-items: stretch;
}

.card {
	background-color: #fff;
	padding: 1em;
	margin: 1em;
	flex: 1 0 300px;
	border-radius: 5px;
	box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.card:hover {
	transform: translateY(-5px);
	box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.card h4 {
	margin-top: 0;
}

.footer {
	background-color: #333;
	color: #fff;
	padding: 1em;
	text-align: center;
}

.footer p {
	margin: 0;
}

	</style>
</head>
<body>

	<header>
		<h1>Decision Maker</h1>
	</header>

	<section class="hero">
		<h2>Can't Make a Decision?</h2>
		<p>Let us help you decide.</p>
		<a href="#" class="cta">Get Started</a>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<h3>What Can We Help You Decide?</h3>
		<div class="card">
			<h4>Where to Eat Dinner Tonight?</h4>
			<p>Can't decide on what to eat for dinner? We've got you covered. Answer a few simple questions and we'll suggest the perfect restaurant for you.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="card">
			<h4>What Types of Jobs to Apply To?</h4>
			<p>Feeling overwhelmed by job listings? We can help you narrow down your search by identifying the types of jobs that best match your skills and interests.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<footer class="footer">
		<p>&copy; 2023 Decision Maker. All rights reserved.</p>
	</footer>

</body>
